law.history: Repealed 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 134, sec. 9, effective July 1, 1994. -- Amended 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 200, sec. 6, effective June 17, 1978. -- Created 1976 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 22, sec. 57, effective January 2, 1978.
